(Awqmk mOq pYdw krn vwlI mwieAw dy) zhr ivc msq hoieAw mnu`K aus zhr ivc hI mgn rihMdw hY ]3]
(ABwgI) mnu`K mwieAw nUM (izMdgI dw) Awsrw bxw ky (mwieAw dI ^wqr hI) Btkdy rihMdy hn,
mwieAw dy ipAwr dy kwrn auhnW nUM prmwqmw BuilAw rihMdw hY[
(pr,) ijs mnu`K au~qy prmwqmw rihm dI ingwh krdw hY, auh mnu`K sB qoN au~cI Awqmk AvsQw hwsl kr lYNdw hY (ij`Qy mwieAw dw moh poh nhIN skdw) ]4]
(jyhVw mnu`K gurU dI srn pYNdw hY, gurU aus dy) ihrdy ivc sdw-iQr rihx vwly prmwqmw dw prkwS kr dyNdw hY, jgq nwl vrqx-vrqwv kridAW BI swry jgq ivc aus nUM sdw-iQr pRBU ivKw dyNdw hY[
(ijs mnu`K dy AMdr bwhr pRBU dw prkwS ho jwey), auh jy ies (imlI dwiq) nUM lukw ky r`Kx dw jqn BI kry qW BI sd-iQr pRBU (dw prkwS) lukdw nhIN[
prmwqmw nwl fUMGI sWJ r`Kx vwly mnu`K Awqmk Afolqw ivc (itk ky) pRBU-pRym ivc juV ky (ies AslIAq nUM) smJ lYNdy hn ]5]
