mYN hr vyly Awpxy ihrdy ivc jgq dy mwlk prmwqmw dw nwm jpdw hW[
gurU dI srn pY ky mYN sB qoN au~cw Awqmk drjw hwsl kr ilAw hY, mYN Awqmk AwnMd mwx irhw hW ]1] rhwau]
