(gurU dI srn pY ky ijs mnu`K dw mn prmwqmw dI Xwd ivc iv`J jWdw hY, auh ieauN Ardws krdw hY-hy pRBU!) qUM hI jgq dw pYdw krn vwlw hYN, mYnUM qYQoN ibnw koeI Awsrw nhIN id`sdw,
